This paper discusses techniques for model generation, which is a problem commonly studied in the field of automated reasoning and logic. The paper specifically focuses on enhancements to bottom-up model generation methods, which are commonly used in formal verification and security protocol analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science).
